really all it means

00:20:12.010 --> 00:20:16.270
is we place a square on
each of the three spikes.

00:20:16.270 --> 00:20:22.210
And the convolution theorem
says that the Fourier transform

00:20:22.210 --> 00:20:26.570
of a convolution is the product
of the Fourier transforms.

00:20:26.570 --> 00:20:30.890
So what you'd expect is that the
Fourier transform that you're

00:20:30.890 --> 00:20:33.560
going to see here is
