these three delta functions

00:21:07.500 --> 00:21:12.830
is 1 plus a cosine, or
something like that.

00:21:12.830 --> 00:21:15.660
And so that's what we
expect to see, then.

00:21:15.660 --> 00:21:19.800
This thing, this pattern
