01:02:03.860 --> 01:02:08.070
And then finally, these
two combined together

01:02:08.070 --> 01:02:10.190
to make a cosine.

01:02:10.190 --> 01:02:13.860
And our final
amplitude of our image

01:02:13.860 --> 01:02:17.370
is going to be a
constant plus of cosine.

01:02:17.370 --> 01:02:19.290
You notice that it's not--

01:02:19.290 --> 01:02:21.420
the amplitude of
this is not the same

01:02:21.420 --> 01:02:24.870
as the amplitude of that, of
