01:23:27.845 --> 01:23:28.655
AUDIENCE: Plus [INAUDIBLE].

01:23:28.655 --> 01:23:30.530
COLIN SHEPPARD: Oh yeah,
OK, so [INAUDIBLE]..

01:23:30.530 --> 01:23:31.640
