01:23:31.640 --> 01:23:36.370
So then twice the
products of these two.

01:23:36.370 --> 01:23:38.402
And-- OK.

01:23:38.402 --> 01:23:41.090
Is that right?

01:23:41.090 --> 01:23:41.590
No, sorry.

01:23:41.590 --> 01:23:42.585
That's not right, is it?

01:23:42.585 --> 01:23:44.585
AUDIENCE: The magnitude
of the first [INAUDIBLE]

01:23:44.585 --> 01:23:47.558
the magnitude of the
